### Frontend — API Client

#### [MODIFY] [api.ts](file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/frontend/src/lib/api.ts)
- `patientApi.delete()` metodu ekleme (soft delete)
- TypeScript tipleri: [Patient](file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/frontend/src/app/%28app%29/patients/page.tsx#5-80), `PatientListResponse` interfaceleri

